text: On April 12, 2004, John Doe met Jane Smith at the Palm Beach Marriott in Florida. The meeting began at 3:00 PM and lasted two hours.
Jane Smith later contacted attorney Robert Miller of Miller & Associates LLP. The call took place on April 15, 2004.
